reviewText: So much fun.  I like it even more every time I see it.  The actors are so good.  Some of the cast members were nominated for Tony awards.  My 7 year old daughter loved it!
My son loves this musical! Good to have it on Blu Ray in case Netflix take it off.

Got it for my family because they wouldn't stop watching it on Netflix and I knew they would be sad when Netflix drops it. Yeah, I enjoy torturing myself. Seller was fantastic and the blue ray was great.
This is an amazing musical that will make you laugh and cheer. My 4 year old daughter loves it!
